        <mxCell id="e7" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.25;entryY=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="pacer" target="ring">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
